      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the<strong> onion wedges </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>to one side of a separate baking tray (or two!) and set aside for later</p>",
