    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas </strong>and add them to a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give them a good mix up – these are your <strong>paprika chickpeas</strong></p>",
